lead_paragraph: Former NFL quarterback Johnny Manziel, who was released by the Cleveland Browns earlier this year due to questionable conduct, has re-enrolled as a student at Texas A&M University, the school said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Former Cleveland Browns Quarterback Manziel Re-enrolls at Texas A&M
